<section id="news" class="page-section team-member news-section">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="heading text-center">
      <h2>News</h2>
      <p>
        Updates from the AiX Lab, including research progress, publications, and people-related achievements.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="news-list">

      <!-- (1) 항상 맨 위: 모집 중 안내 (가장 최신) -->
      <article class="news-card">
        <h3 class="news-card-title">AiX Lab – 학부/석사/박사 과정 모집 안내</h3>
        <p class="news-card-meta">Updated: 2025</p>
        <div class="news-card-body">
          <p>
            AiX Lab은 <strong>학부연구생</strong>, <strong>석사과정</strong>, 
            <strong>박사과정</strong>, <strong>석·박 통합과정</strong> 지원자를 모집하고 있습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            주요 연구 분야는 <strong>Medical AI</strong>, 
            <strong>Autonomous Driving (F1TENTH / RoboRacer)</strong>, 
            <strong>AI Safety &amp; CPS Verification</strong>입니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            자세한 모집 요강 및 지원 양식은 아래 페이지에서 확인하실 수 있습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            🔗 <a href="https://aix.gnu.ac.kr/join.html" target="_blank">
            https://aix.gnu.ac.kr/join.html</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- (2) NeurIPS 2025 참가 -->
      <article class="news-card">
        <h3 class="news-card-title">NeurIPS 2025 – Conference Participation</h3>
        <p class="news-card-meta">Dec 2–7, 2025 · San Diego Convention Center</p>
        <div class="news-card-body">
          <p>
            미국 샌디에이고에서 열린 <strong>NeurIPS 2025</strong>에  
            <strong>김진현</strong>, <strong>조민아</strong>, <strong>조은아</strong>가 참가했습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            LLM Safety, World Models, Medical AI 세션 및 워크숍에 집중 참여하며 
            향후 연구 방향과 공동 연구 기회를 모색했습니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- (3) Publications – SCI(E) 4편 게재 -->
      <article class="news-card">
        <h3 class="news-card-title">2025 – SCI(E) 논문 4편 게재 완료</h3>
        <p class="news-card-meta">2025</p>
        <div class="news-card-body">
          <p>
            2025년에 총 <strong>4편의 SCI(E) 논문</strong>이 게재 또는 출판 승인되었습니다 
            (IEEE Access 2편, Scientific Reports 2편).
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Soomin Cho, Inhye Kang, Kim, Jin Hyun.</strong><br>
              “From Timed Automata to Go: Formally Verified Code Generation and Runtime Monitoring for Cyber-Physical Systems.”<br>
              <em>IEEE Access, 13:161729–161749, 2025.</em>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Kim, Jin Hyun et al.</strong><br>
              “Low-Cost and Fast Epiretinal Membrane Detection and Quantification Based on SD-OCT.”<br>
              <em>IEEE Access, Accepted for Publication, 2025.</em>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Kim, Jin Hyun et al.</strong><br>
              “Noise-Robust Markerless Video Gait Anomaly Detection via Two-Stage Acquisition and LSTM Autoencoders.”<br>
              <em>Scientific Reports, Accepted for Publication, 2025.</em>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Kim, Jin Hyun et al.</strong><br>
              “Ophtimus-V2-Tx: A Compact Domain-Specific LLM for Ophthalmic Diagnosis and Treatment Planning.”<br>
              <em>Scientific Reports, Accepted for Publication, 2025.</em>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- (4) Research Highlights -->
      <article class="news-card">
        <h3 class="news-card-title">Research Highlights</h3>
        <p class="news-card-meta">2025</p>
        <div class="news-card-body">
          <p>
            AiX Lab은 <strong>Medical AI</strong>, <strong>Autonomous Driving</strong>, 
            <strong>AI Safety &amp; CPS Verification</strong> 분야에서
            여러 연구 과제를 동시에 수행하고 있습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            F1TENTH / RoboRacer 기반 자율주행 레이싱, 안과 영상 정량화, 
            포멀 메서드 기반 CPS 검증 및 코드 생성/모니터링 연구 등이 포함됩니다.
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- (5) People & Alumni -->
      <article class="news-card">
        <h3 class="news-card-title">People &amp; Alumni News</h3>
        <p class="news-card-meta">2025</p>
        <div class="news-card-body">
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Minwook Kwon (M.S., Aug. 2025)</strong> – 
              <a href="https://www.publicai.co.kr/" target="_blank">Public AI</a> 입사 (AI Engineer).
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Seungju Baek (M.S., Mar. 2025)</strong> – 
              <a href="https://www.saltlux.com/" target="_blank">Saltlux</a> 합류, 
              재학 중 <strong>Ophtimus</strong> 안과 LLM 연구에 핵심 기여.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


